      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Operator Flow\n- Start here to answer: what is broken, how broad is it, and which worker should I open next.\n- Use the top stats for immediate posture.\n- Read **Active Failure Clusters** and **Active Failure x Runtime Counts** to see whether breakage is isolated or shared, and whether it aligns with unhealthy runtime snapshots.\n- Use **Active Failure x Runtime Workers** to choose a worker, then switch to **Drilldown Dashboard** or **Selected Worker**.\n- Use **Fleet Workload Shapes** to confirm whether the issue clusters around a replay dataset or load profile.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Start Here",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
